{
  "stem": "3631.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then, in connection with what's going on in the world today, in Somalia, and Yugoslavia, and Luanda, and all these places, where there are wars, and there are people killed just because of hatred, or intolerance, or-- or just ignorance, or-- that it is so important that these things be preserved in, like the tape, what I speak today, that these things will be preserved and brought to the people's knowledge, that they see what can happen, if these things are not controlled.",
      "word_count": 84
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Whether it will succeed, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Maybe it's a utopia, that you could never have peace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But-- but you have to try.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I feel very strongly about it, that people should be told that there were good people who helped, who-- who did-- who were not bystanders.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were millions of people who-- who didn't actively take part, but who were bystanders-- let-- let it happen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were a few people who-- like Schindler, or like [INAUDIBLE], or the-- the-- the-- the Polish woman that smuggled some milk into the camp-- they-- they became rescuers to us.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I think it's important.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were not born heroes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "These were just plain, ordinary people, but who found they-- they had that sense that something has to be done when they saw something wrong.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I think that has to be-- that thought has to be told to the world.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When I met Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Schindler, and she was in Palm Beach, in Florida, in November, we met her at a reception.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And it was quite an-- I saw her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "After 50 years, she's a woman of 87 years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And she said to me a couple of things.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
